Class RandomizedQueue<Item>

  • java.lang.Object
    • RandomizedQueue<Item>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Item>

    public class RandomizedQueue<Item>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Item>
    Randomized Queue Implements a queue or stack like structure with access methods that uniformly at random sample or remove from the data structure The API here is designed by Robert Sedgewick and Kevin Wayne as part of their online Coursera class. For more resources, see the Algorithms homepage.
    Author:
    Bryan Goodrich
